title: Site-wide emergency evacuation exercise underway (ANSTO - Australian Nuclear Science and Technology Organisation)
text: ( Source : ANSTO - Australian Nuclear Science and Technology Organisation ) The Australian Nuclear Science and Technology Organisation (ANSTO) is now conducting a site-wide bushfire evacuation exercise at its Lucas Heights facility today
